<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="aff15Dec1938"><font color="red">15 December 1938</font> <i>NLFF</i> (from Richard de la Mere to Paul L&eacute;on): I was glad to have the batch that I received from you this morning, the 30 galleys to follow on page 355. Yes, I think it best perhaps to complete the correction on the remaining galleys in advance of the page proofs that you still have &hellip; </div>
